      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the general vibe. To make it more realistic for the screenplay, I want to add some tension or specific character dynamics. Since it's a multi-generational family, how would the different generations interact during this dinner? Like, are there specific ways the younger kids act vs the elders, or any common types of arguments or topics that usually come up in these kinds of family settings?",
